        <p>Mother’s Day is a very special occasion for moms celebrating their very first year being a <script>function ga4_link95() { window.dataLayer.push(JSON.parse('{"event":"click_inarticle"}')) }</script><a href="https://reviewed.usatoday.com/gift-guides/features/gifts-for-mom" onclick="ga4_link95()">mom</a>! Classic gifts like <script>function ga4_link96() { window.dataLayer.push(JSON.parse('{"event":"click_inarticle"}')) }</script><a href="https://reviewed.usatoday.com/home-outdoors/features/12-best-places-order-flowers-online" onclick="ga4_link96()">flowers</a> and <script>function ga4_link97() { window.dataLayer.push(JSON.parse('{"event":"click_inarticle"}')) }</script><a href="https://reviewed.usatoday.com/gift-guides/features/jewelry-gifts-for-moms" onclick="ga4_link97()">jewelry</a> are always solid options for Mother’s Day, but if you’re shopping for first Mother’s Day gift ideas, you might want to get her an extra-special gift to commemorate her new title. </p>

<p>There are lots of thoughtful first Mother’s Day gifts to choose from, whether it’s a <script>function ga4_link98() { window.dataLayer.push(JSON.parse('{"event":"default_event"}')) }</script><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/gannett_bb334_reviewed?author=Camryn+Rabideau&amp;content_id=36449&amp;event_type=click&amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Freviewed.usatoday.com%2Fgift-guides%2Ffeatures%2Ffirst-mothers-day-gifts-new-moms&amp;pub_date=2024-03-04T18%3A20%3A05Z&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D83224X1595658%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3DREV-LST-GFG-%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.etsy.com%252Flisting%252F1162257926%252Fmommy-handprint-footprint-art-craft" onclick="ga4_link98()" data-trackonomics="">custom craft from her baby</a>, a delicious <script>function ga4_link99() { window.dataLayer.push(JSON.parse('{"event":"default_event"}')) }</script><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/gannett_bb334_reviewed?author=Camryn+Rabideau&amp;content_id=36449&amp;event_type=click&amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Freviewed.usatoday.com%2Fgift-guides%2Ffeatures%2Ffirst-mothers-day-gifts-new-moms&amp;pub_date=2024-03-04T18%3A20%3A05Z&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D83224X1595658%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3DREV-LST-GFG-%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fcompartes.com%252Fproducts%252Fcorporate-gourmet-chocolate-gift-tower" onclick="ga4_link99()" data-trackonomics="">tower of handmade chocolates</a> to devour after a long day, or a <script>function ga4_link100() { window.dataLayer.push(JSON.parse('{"event":"default_event"}')) }</script><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/gannett_bb334_reviewed?author=Camryn+Rabideau&amp;content_id=36449&amp;event_type=click&amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Freviewed.usatoday.com%2Fgift-guides%2Ffeatures%2Ffirst-mothers-day-gifts-new-moms&amp;pub_date=2024-03-04T18%3A20%3A05Z&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D83224X1595658%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3DREV-LST-GFG-%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.etsy.com%252Flisting%252F587062695%252Fpersonalised-my-mum-book-for-moth